<html lang="en">
	<!-- # para id, . para class Descendant rule es un espacio -->
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Astro</title>
		<style>
			*{
				border: 1px solid red;
			}
			body {
				margin: 0;
			}
			img {
				width: 100px;
			}
			#mountain-image {
				width: 50px;
			}
			#title {
				font-family: sans-serif;
				color: blue;
			}
			.special {
				background-color: pink;
			}
			.highlighted {
				outline: 5px solid yellow;
				outline-offset: 5px;
			}
			li.highlighted {
				outline-color: blue;
			}
			p em {
				text-decoration: underline;
				font-style: normal;
				color: brown;
			}
			.abstract {
				border: 2px solid black;
				padding: 10px;
				font-family: sans-serif;
			}
			.abstract em {
				color: blue;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1 id="title">Astro!!!!</h1>
		<div class="special highlighted">
			<h2>This is an image</h2>
			<img
				id="mountain-image"
				src="images/nature.jpg"
				alt="A picture of a landscape with a sea"
			/>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h2>This is an SVG (V1)</h2>
			<img class="highlighted" src="favicon.svg" alt="Logo of Astro" />
		</div>
		<div class="special">
			<h2>This is an SVG (V2)</h2>
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 128 128">
				<path
					d="M50.4 78.5a75.1 75.1 0 0 0-28.5 6.9l24.2-65.7c.7-2 1.9-3.2 3.4-3.2h29c1.5 0 2.7 1.2 3.4 3.2l24.2 65.7s-11.6-7-28.5-7L67 45.5c-.4-1.7-1.6-2.8-2.9-2.8-1.3 0-2.5 1.1-2.9 2.7L50.4 78.5Zm-1.1 28.2Zm-4.2-20.2c-2 6.6-.6 15.8 4.2 20.2a17.5 17.5 0 0 1 .2-.7 5.5 5.5 0 0 1 5.7-4.5c2.8.1 4.3 1.5 4.7 4.7.2 1.1.2 2.3.2 3.5v.4c0 2.7.7 5.2 2.2 7.4a13 13 0 0 0 5.7 4.9v-.3l-.2-.3c-1.8-5.6-.5-9.5 4.4-12.8l1.5-1a73 73 0 0 0 3.2-2.2 16 16 0 0 0 6.8-11.4c.3-2 .1-4-.6-6l-.8.6-1.6 1a37 37 0 0 1-22.4 2.7c-5-.7-9.7-2-13.2-6.2Z"
				></path>
				<style>
					path {
						fill: rgb(255, 102, 0);
					}
					@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
						path {
							fill: #fff;
						}
					}
				</style>
			</svg>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h2>This is an <code>ordered list</code></h2>
			<ol type="1">
				<li class="highlighted" value="5">First</li>
				<li>Second</li>
				<li>Third</li>
			</ol>
			<div>
				<h2>This is an <code class="special">unordered list</code></h2>
				<ul>
					<li class="special">alpha</li>
					<li>beta</li>
					<li>gamma</li>
					<li>
						Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Quae
						maiores corrupti laudantium distinctio in optio, exercitationem
						veritatis voluptas omnis excepturi alias sequi quaerat tempore
						nesciunt ex debitis rem explicabo? Voluptas.
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<p class="abstract">
				Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Voluptatibus
				et eveniet, nisi perferendis <em>quibusdam</em> illum. Quos iusto labore
				enim totam libero, cupiditate quae, veniam nisi aperiam at itaque perspiciatis
				suscipit!
			</p>
			<p>
				Lorem ipsum <em> dolor</em> sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quibusdam
				expedita autem eveniet at porro minima aperiam ut! Asperiores, esse facilis
				cumque optio perspiciatis excepturi consequuntur omnis vero, fugiat error
				consectetur!
			</p>
			<div style="height: 25rem"></div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
